{"tid":145290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港d公公婆婆話，共產黨解放軍好好人㗎","createTime":"2017-03-06T06:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T09:40:18.000Z","uid":71949,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b51e02506147f9766a53fa1dab900203eead9f5","tid":145290,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"文革果陣佢地話唔差，得閒會同你打下橋牌同叫你教佢背毛語錄，佢地對毛澤東事蹟同香港史好有興趣。不過，佢地會定期搜尋抗共隊，只要你守規矩就冇事，知道有國軍就指證會有錢獎，就算搵唔到游擊隊都係嘈2句巡完村就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外解放軍會派下糖俾細路，同徵召平民去修路大煉鋼，有d仲會去礦物做，工錢高過國民黨治區添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:轉自奴隸狗，中意奶人屎眼改編，<br />\n我反支架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e92497439482c975c0b3b48907c6792d02cf065","tid":145290,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ab6eff54abd6ef238a08b657193d7d61d0c8b0","tid":145290,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:08:53.000Z","msg":"聽阿公講 共產黨批鬥完成個家族 燒埋祖屋之後<br />\n都有提供免費教育俾啲細路 好好人架"},{"pid":"decabc385df4c64d31ef36b3e8471513979c527a","tid":145290,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:28:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽阿公講 共產黨批鬥完成個家族 燒埋祖屋之後<br />\n都有提供免費教育俾啲細路 好好人架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀，我爺爺話64果時解放軍有份安撫民眾，示威者和平散去，一個人都冇死到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話有人死都係日本編造出黎，共產黨真係好好人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6d826a63ea178730769ba8355d209618711ab2","tid":145290,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:36:42.000Z","msg":"聽爺爺講文革同64殺人果D解放軍係韓國籍軍人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔關中國人事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba2cfe47bc6